eaders of the Greek War of Independence]]\n", "name_user": "CapJoe2", "label": "safe", "comment": "I removed the images as advised by the Greek wiki editors and kept the birth registry office but it\u2019s in Greek so I'm not sure If that's ok. Sorry in advance.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kassotis_family"}
